# PB138: Drill

## Drills Collection [/drill]

### List all drills [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "drills": [
                {
                    "id": "123",
                    "name": "PB138"
                }
            ]
        }

### Create new drill [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "PB138"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /drill/123

    + Body

            {
                "id": "123",
                "name": "PB138"
            }

