## Exam Collection [/user/{user_id}/exam]

+ Parameters

    + user_id (number) - ID of relevant user
    
### Create new exam [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "drill_id": "123"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /user/{user_id}/exam/1

    + Body
    
            {
                "id": 1,
                "drill_id": 123,
                "answers": [ 
                    { "question_id": 44, "correct": 0, "incorrect": 0 }
                ]
            }
            
### List all exams [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "exams": [
                    {
                        "id": 1,
                        "drill_id": 123,
                        "answers": [ 
                            { "question_id": 44, "correct": 0, "incorrect": 0 }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }


            
